# Web Interface Guidelines

## FastAPI Application Structure
- Main app: [app.py](mdc:app.py)
- Static files served from `static/` directory
- File uploads handled in `uploads/` directory
- Outputs generated in `outputs/` directory

## API Endpoints
- `GET /` - Main web interface
- `POST /upload` - File upload and conversion
- `GET /download/{filename}` - Download converted files

## Frontend Design Principles
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop
- Modern, clean UI with intuitive navigation
- Drag-and-drop file upload support
- Real-time progress feedback
- Error handling with user-friendly messages

## File Handling
- Validate file types (PDF only)
- Implement proper file cleanup
- Use secure file naming conventions
- Handle large file uploads gracefully

## User Experience
- Provide clear instructions in Chinese and English
- Show conversion progress and status
- Offer preview of converted content
- Enable easy download of results

## Security Considerations
- Validate uploaded files
- Sanitize file names
- Implement proper error handling
- Avoid exposing sensitive file paths
